body_html: This seems to be a bug in your code rather than with TensorFlow itself. Due to the huge volume of issues the TensorFlow team isn't able to provide help on this type of situation but only to bugs with TensorFlow or feature requests on Github. This question is better suited for StackOverflow which is also monitored under the TensorFlow tag.
